# Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# NEVER commit .env.local to git
#
# All credentials are stored in localStorage via the Settings page.
# This file documents the shape of config — no actual secrets here.
#
# Schwab: appKey, appSecret, refreshToken → stored under cfg_schwab
# OKX:    apiKey, secret, passphrase     → stored under cfg_okx
# Zerion: apiKey, walletAddresses        → stored under cfg_zerion
# Finnhub: apiKey                        → stored under cfg_finnhub
# Google Sheets: spreadsheetId, sheetsApiKey → stored under cfg_gsheets
